{"tid":421934,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"踢波鐘意踢大場定細場？","createTime":"2017-10-02T15:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T17:35:21.000Z","uid":141957,"like":19,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"75a231d461b9cbb0423d593726733321ad4eb4e5","tid":421934,"uid":141957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"大場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大場即係要book個隻草地嘅size<br />\n細場就普遍街埸硬地嘅size<br />\n大場就比較講體能，組織<br />\n細埸比較講個人技術"},{"pid":"bf9ba94877016b70a3999be131b1d5d2c307a5dc","tid":421934,"uid":141957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:45:20.000Z","msg":"正皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25649654f4afe0e8ce6ae0c16033b1d0360da889","tid":421934,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"大場好玩啲，但要成隊都好意識先踢得掂<br />\n細場玩技術多，失位易啲補"},{"pid":"19076340103164f6d666c08f404cad4d6cf83464","tid":421934,"uid":141957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:52:20.000Z","msg":"太夜無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b610b60fbb9dc4b04cadea291779a372841fdd","tid":421934,"uid":53543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:56:41.000Z","msg":"大場先冇咁攰，個場大唔係好多但多左四個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你打防中另計<br />\n打七人先攰到仆街，基本上除左中堅龍門全隊都要跑上跑落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申跑多兩部都扯蝦"},{"pid":"bc177fe101004cb31aa6d90e94aee877d32af361","tid":421934,"uid":53543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大場先冇咁攰，個場大唔係好多但多左四個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你打防中另計<br />\n打七人先攰到仆街，基本上除左中堅龍門全隊都要跑上跑落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申跑多兩部都扯蝦</blockquote><br />\n同埋大場好似多啲時間俾你做決定，細場基本上波都未拎就差唔多有人拍到黎 可能我廢鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d882d00a66194cdb7e2e83290916871ca9b45e8d","tid":421934,"uid":48521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大場先冇咁攰，個場大唔係好多但多左四個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你打防中另計<br />\n打七人先攰到仆街，基本上除左中堅龍門全隊都要跑上跑落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申跑多兩部都扯蝦</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n除非你係打比賽<br />\n唔係踢大場都一係攻一係守啦"},{"pid":"c4acfbef744cd62112b4b03745f1903d80522e2e","tid":421934,"uid":141957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大場先冇咁攰，個場大唔係好多但多左四個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你打防中另計<br />\n打七人先攰到仆街，基本上除左中堅龍門全隊都要跑上跑落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申跑多兩部都扯蝦</blockquote><br />\n大唔係好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282916ac6c7a5e5a4d061b4db0d9c4789fce8e02","tid":421934,"uid":141957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大場先冇咁攰，個場大唔係好多但多左四個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你打防中另計<br />\n打七人先攰到仆街，基本上除左中堅龍門全隊都要跑上跑落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申跑多兩部都扯蝦</blockquote><br />\n大唔係好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/000118_259441839862fb4dd022693c49fa4fd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F000118_259441839862fb4dd022693c49fa4fd5.jpg&h=c345e80f&s={SIZ